'''Miguel A. Fuertes''' is a computer graphics animator and digital artist. He worked on the [[Star Wars video games|video game]]s ''[[Star Wars: Bounty Hunter]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II]]''. He was also the lead animator with [[Industrial Light & Magic|ILM]] for [[Sebulba/Legends|Sebulba]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']].

Other notable work includes [[Wikipedia:Casper (film)|''Casper'']], [[Wikipedia:Jurassic Park (film)|''Jurassic Park'']], and [[Wikipedia:Happy Feet|''Happy Feet'']].

He was born in [[Wikipedia:Madrid|Madrid]], [[Wikipedia:Spain|Spain]] on [[October 30]], [[1950s|1957]].

